data.description: Beautiful, well maintained home in a quiet cul de sac. Open floor plan with crown molding throughout main living areas. Beautifully maintained backyard with a  gorgeous patio with 2 Gazebos, and a spa (which is negotiable). Kitchen features Smart Samsung suite of appliances, and a large pantry.  New Roof in 2022. Custom blinds, and bench in primary bedroom, along with Tray Ceilings. Luxury Vinyl Tile flooring throughout.  Fully renovated bathrooms with modern LED light fixtures and ceiling fans. Near shopping, schools, and easy access to US 73.
